 doubts upon proposals that the carriers of\nthese features are the same as those of DIBs seen at slightly shorter\nwavelengths.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 17 Jan 2020 17:00:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-02-05"}
