 that finding this plane in real galaxies\ncan provide insights into the velocity direction.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 17 Jan 2020 19:07:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 3 Feb 2020 18:20:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-02-19"}
