rce redshift and the time-lags given by\ndifferent astrophysical processes of the binary NS merger, we find that our\nconstraints are not sensitive to the redshift in the range of (0.005, 0.01) and\nthe time-lag in the range of (-100s, 1.734s).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 18 Jan 2020 02:46:27 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 4 Jun 2020 09:29:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-06-05"}
