gains compared\nto the beam sweeping used in 5G standard is proposed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 18 Jan 2020 04:07:49 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 28 May 2020 17:54:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-05-29"}
